<figureCitation id="8A9617AFCED0C8655A1A9AD2F472B2B8" captionStart="Figures 49–50" captionStartId="F14" captionText="Figures 49 - 50.. 47 Semiardistomis major sp. n. 50 Semiardistomis rugosus (Putzeys). Dorsal aspect. Scale bar 1 mm." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/19672" pageId="18" pageNumber="37">Fig. 50</figureCitation>
