</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="AF319CC863018BAB0ECFF29BE29E6E75" pageId="19" pageNumber="38" type="measurements and variation">
<paragraph id="4CBEAB61C649A8739D4D02BA551E49D7" pageId="19" pageNumber="38">
<pageBreakToken id="A893EAA8C8DD22CD5D26AC87F23AC3DE" pageId="19" pageNumber="38" start="start">Measurements</pageBreakToken>
and variation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7A410C0A8FD76D4C4D9894521956ED81" pageId="19" pageNumber="38">
Variation of measurements (mm) and ratios for 
<taxonomicName id="3842A363D56CB66269BA7C546277938E" baseAuthorityName="Putzeys" baseAuthorityYear="1866" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Semiardistomis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="38" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rugosus">
<emphasis id="9470B6180AC9639C79B34138207BA5FD" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="38">Semiardistomis rugosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(n=2) are: HL = 0,71; PL = 1,35; PW = 1,51; EL = 3,72-3,73-3,75; EW = 2,34-2,42-2,50; 
<emphasis id="B2B844ED5F1FCBFA86566D7B91993BCC" bold="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="38">SBL =</emphasis>
5,78; PW/EW = 0,64; PW/PL = 1,12; PL/EL = 0,36; EW/EL = 0,63.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
